00:20.800 --> 00:21.830
我们就是来保护你的
That's what we're here for.

00:21.830 --> 00:23.700
我可以用支票来买吗 因为我没有...
Can I write a check for the food? 'Cause I don't have...

00:23.700 --> 00:26.660
你好  荷兰德夫人
hello,mrs.Hollander.

