it'll be the last thing they ever do.

00:41.800 --> 00:42.700
保罗 克里曼带了一组人
Paul Kellerman has a team

00:42.700 --> 00:44.160
正在往囚车那里赶
ready to move on the caravan

00:44.160 --> 00:45.330
就在阿尔伯克基市的市郊
just outside of Albuquerque.

00:45.330 --> 00:46.560
当他们动手的时候
When it goes down,

00:46.560 --> 00:48.000
