there's sure to be lots of bullets flying.

00:48.000 --> 00:52.660
我要你去确保保罗 克里曼  被乱飞的子弹射中
I need you there to make sure Paul Kellerman catches one.

00:58.030 --> 00:59.800
雷纳德总统毁了你们的人生
President Reynolds ruined your life.

00:59.800 --> 01:01.930
她也毁了我的
She ruined my life.

01:01.930 --> 01:03.300
你们想把那贱人拉下台?
You want to take the bitch down,

01:03.300 --> 01:04.900
你们刚刚找到了个内部盟友
you just found your inside man,

01:04.900 --> 01:06.830
但我们现在必须马上走
but it's got to be right now.Let's go!

01:22.100 --> 01:25.100
我知道出去的路
I know the way out!

01:44.700 --> 01:47.660
我需要一队在西面包抄
I want a team flanking west.

01:47.660 --> 01:51.400
派另一队到河边去
Give me another team down by the river.

01:57.760 --> 01:58.830
