02:08.130 --> 02:11.500
我是塔格尔警官
Officer Tuggle.

02:11.560 --> 02:14.300
塔格尔警官
Officer Tuggle?

02:14.300 --> 02:17.160
我在找亚历山大 马宏
I'm looking for Alexander Mahone.

02:17.160 --> 02:18.360
