or you get me your supervisor.

03:15.500 --> 03:16.930
这里的路障由我来负责
I'm supervising this roadblock,

03:16.930 --> 03:18.430
克里曼  特工
agent Kellerman.

03:18.430 --> 03:22.030
很抱歉  我希望你能够先下来
I'm sorry, but I need you to get out of the vehicle.

03:22.030 --> 03:24.460
警官  呃
Sergeant, uh, Humphries.

03:24.460 --> 03:26.360
林肯 布伦斯和迈克尔 斯科菲尔德
Burrows and Scofield

03:26.360 --> 03:27.660
在这不到十分钟内已经跑掉了
have been on the loose for less than ten minutes.

03:27.660 --> 03:30.460
