It was very peaceful.

04:21.760 --> 04:26.790
嘘 嘘 嘘  前一分钟它还在呼吸  后一分钟  它就断气了
Shh-shh-shh! One minute she was breatng. The next, she wasn't.

04:29.960 --> 04:33.220
转过来
Turn around.

04:48.930 --> 04:50.090
起来
get up!

04:50.090 --> 04:52.910
起来
Get up!

