Give me one good reason why I shouldn't blow your brains out!

04:55.500 --> 04:59.250
因为我能给你们  唯一能让你们脱罪的东西
Because I can give you the one thing that's gonna set you free.

04:59.250 --> 05:03.250
我知道特伦斯  斯蒂德曼在哪里
I know where Terrence Steadman is.

05:42.040 --> 05:44.020
你怎么知道斯蒂德曼在哪里
how do you know where Steadman is?

05:44.020 --> 05:46.240
