Because I arranged this whole thing.

05:46.240 --> 05:48.060
是你策划陷害了我  没错
- You arranged to set me up?- That's right.

05:48.060 --> 05:50.980
是你策划杀死了我身边所有的人
You arranged the killing of all the people I know.

05:50.980 --> 05:53.080
