I was given orders, I executed those orders,

05:53.080 --> 05:57.420
而现在我也被当成靶子追杀  和你们一样
and now I have a bull's-eye on my chest,just like you two.

05:57.420 --> 06:00.800
我不相信他
I don't trust him.

06:03.520 --> 06:07.750
如果我真想让你  你早死了
If I wanted you dead, you'd be dead.

06:07.750 --> 06:10.010
你们想继续逃亡  没问题
You guys want to keep running, fine.

06:10.010 --> 06:12.830
你们想洗脱罪名  就上车
You want to be free, get in the car.

06:12.830 --> 06:16.480
我只说最后一次
Last time I'm gonna offer.

06:18.590 --> 06:21.190
伊利诺伊州  福克斯河监狱
Joliet, Illinois Fox River penitentiary

06:41.750 --> 06:45.190
怎么了  菜鸟
What's up, fish?

06:48.260 --> 06:51.540
看来你日子挺难熬嘛
Looks like you're having a tough time of it.

06:51.540 --> 06:52.670
我很好
I'm all right.

06:52.670 --> 06:55.260
