Well, I'm just curious.

06:55.260 --> 07:00.180
你怎么不和其他"前狱警"在一起啊
Why don't you hang out with the rest of the ex-guards that are locked up here?

07:00.180 --> 07:02.050
哦  对了
oh, yeah.

07:02.050 --> 07:03.920
这里没有前狱警
There ain't any.

07:03.920 --> 07:07.390
你就是那独苗
It's just you.

07:11.140 --> 07:13.620
嘿  等等 等等
hey, ho-ho-hold up, hold up.

07:13.620 --> 07:17.320
我想到一个双赢互利的安排
now, I got what's called a mutual beneficial arrangement in my mind.

07:17.320 --> 07:20.940
我会罩着你  确保没人找你麻烦
I'll look out after you,make sure nobody get up in your mix.

07:20.940 --> 07:25.390
你要做的就是下餐饭后  把甜点带给我
And all you got to do is bring me your dessert after the next meal.

07:25.390 --> 07:26.640
简单极了
It's real simple.

07:26.640 --> 07:29.460
我只是想赶快服完刑  不想找任何麻烦
I'm just looking to do my time.I don't want any trouble.

07:29.460 --> 07:33.880
是啊  你有你想要的  我有我想要的
Yeah, there's what you want,and there's what I want.

07:33.880 --> 07:37.010
下顿饭的甜点
Your dessert after the next chow.

07:37.010 --> 07:39.840
给我送过来  明白吗
You bring it to me. You got it?

07:39.840 --> 07:42.920
不  你找错人了
No. Wrong guy.

07:42.920 --> 07:45.560
嘿  住手  犯人
Hey! Break it up, convicts!

07:45.560 --> 07:50.210
我们没事的  头儿  没事
We're good, boss. We're good.

07:51.710 --> 07:56.420
要么给我进贡  要么尝尝更厉害的
you bring me my treats,or else this goes next level.

07:56.420 --> 08:00.260
你听明白了吗
Do you understand?

08:01.310 --> 08:05.410
他问你话呢  小子
He asked you a question, boy.

08:06.280 --> 08:08.260
明白了
Yeah.

08:08.260 --> 08:11.560
我没听到  你呢  我也没听到
I ain't hear him. You hear him?-I ain't hear him.

08:11.560 --> 08:13.210
明白了  好的
Yeah, okay.

08:13.210 --> 08:16.930
看看这多简单啊
See how easy that was?

08:16.940 --> 08:20.910
这对我俩都好
We're gonna be good friends, man.

08:36.700 --> 08:38.900
堪萨斯州
Ness City, Kansas

08:38.900 --> 08:42.660
苏茜  你没什么好害怕的
There's no reason for you to be scared, Susie Q.

08:42.760 --> 08:45.530
因为我已经原谅了你
'Cause you see, I've forgiven you.

08:45.530 --> 08:48.760
反过来你也应该原谅我
And you, in turn, can forgive me

08:48.760 --> 08:50.200
原谅我的轻率
for my indiscretions,

08:50.200 --> 08:51.630
现在看来那段曾经
which are so far in the past,

08:51.630 --> 08:56.900
在我们各自回忆当中 不过是瑕疵而已
they're nothingbut specks in our respective rearviews.

08:58.460 --> 09:00.560
过了这么久
It's been such a long time.

09:00.560 --> 09:05.700
你看起来还是如此美丽
You look lovely.

09:06.200 --> 09:07.460
好吧
Okay.

09:07.460 --> 09:09.700
我们走  现在就走
Let's go, right now.

09:09.700 --> 09:11.800
我们...  我们能远走高飞
We can, we can go away,

09:11.800 --> 09:13.730
共度美好的时光
spend some time together.

09:13.730 --> 09:15.030
我又不是老式的手摇留声机
Listen, I'm not a victrola,

09:15.030 --> 09:17.160
