so please don't play me like one.

09:17.160 --> 09:20.460
在黑人社区你不会丢下自己的孩子
There's not a white man's chance in Harlem you'd ever leave your children behind.

09:20.460 --> 09:23.260
跟一个白人私奔
leave your children behind.

09:23.260 --> 09:24.600
对不起
I'm sorry.

09:24.600 --> 09:28.460
别担心
Don't fret now.

09:28.460 --> 09:32.130
你来福克斯河看我那次
When you came to Fox River,

09:32.130 --> 09:33.900
你很生气的向我吐口水
and you spat at me

09:33.900 --> 09:38.400
就好像我是一头...狂恶的畜牲
like I was some kind of. . . rabid animal. . .

09:41.560 --> 09:44.530
其实我很高兴
I was happy.

09:44.530 --> 09:47.030
因为这样的动作发自内心
'Cause such a visceral reaction could only come

09:47.030 --> 09:50.260
说明这个女人依然在意
from a woman who still cares.

09:51.630 --> 09:52.960
孩子们是一无所知的
