09:52.960 --> 09:54.930
我不愿让他们害怕 所以我从没告诉他们
The children don't know anything.I didn't want to scare them,

09:54.930 --> 09:56.330
关于你的事情 所以求你...
so I never told them about you,so please don'T.

09:56.330 --> 10:01.000
简直太完美了
That is so perfect.

10:02.200 --> 10:07.100
