'Cause you see what we got here now?

10:07.800 --> 10:11.760
我们给自己留下了一条清白的道路
We got ourselves a clean slate.

10:11.760 --> 10:15.600
不是吗
Right?

10:20.230 --> 10:22.630
那么这就是整个阴谋
So,this is the conspiracy,huh?

10:22.630 --> 10:24.830
这些西装革履的人 像一群小男孩那样相互追逐
Bunch of little boys in suits running around,

10:24.830 --> 10:27.000
