10:27.000 --> 10:28.430
真是悲哀
It's pathetic.

10:28.430 --> 10:31.930
你比我们预想的要难对付一些
Well,you were a little more formidable than we anticipated.

10:31.930 --> 10:34.530
蠢货  我们不稀罕你的恭维
We don't need compliments out of you,jackass.

10:34.530 --> 10:36.530
是啊  看见了吗
Oh,yes,there it is,

10:36.530 --> 10:38.130
布伦斯吸的人格魅力
the winning burrows personality.

10:38.130 --> 10:39.330
闭上你的嘴  开车
Shut your mouth and drive.

10:39.330 --> 10:41.130
哪怕是陪审团也会被你征服
The one we really knew would win over a jury.

10:41.130 --> 10:44.230
