A "thank you.”

11:32.060 --> 11:36.160
他们尸体入土之后 我会向你汇报的
I'll report back when they're in the ground.

11:36.330 --> 11:38.400
你把手机开着会被他追踪到的
You leave that on,he'll trace it.

11:38.400 --> 11:44.400
是啊  密勤局的电话无法追踪  谢谢
Yeah,uh,secret service. It's untraceable. Thanks.

12:00.060 --> 12:04.260
