I don't believe you.

12:33.200 --> 12:36.730
蒂蒂
Dede! Dede!

12:44.900 --> 12:46.860
是我啊  兄弟
Yo,trey,it's me,man.

12:46.860 --> 12:48.030
怎么了
What's up?

